TIM                                 *222#

Saving changes to the Address Book database...
Done.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

EXAMPLE 3:
Running again, only "Banco Real" needs changes.
The others were already fixed.
Now using "a" to change everything automatically.
=================================================

$ ./change_ddd.py
Auto Elétrica Akio     (099 43) 3376-8838
